inancial%20stability.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20found%20ways%20to%20save%20on%20insurance%20and%20other%20bills%2C%20and%20we%20streamlined%20our%20remaining%20debts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20read%20a%20lot%20of%20books%20about%20personal%20finance%20and%20learned%20as%20much%20as%20we%20could%20about%20our%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20my%20now-husband%20Marshall%20and%20I%20officially%20tied%20the%20knot%2C%20one%20important%20stipulation%20was%20getting%20our%20finances%20in%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20my%20husband%20did%20that%20was%20by%20consolidating%20his%20loans%20to%20get%20out%20of%20debt.%20This%20included%20consumer%20spending%2C%20auto%20loans%2C%20and%20health%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20six%20months%2C%20Marshall%20increased%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fwhat-is-a-good-credit-score%5C%22%3Ecredit%20score%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20630%20to%20750%2C%20mainly%20by%20consolidating%20multiple%20credit%20cards%20and%20an%20auto%20loan%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-loans%2Fbest-debt-consolidation-loans%5C%22%3Edebt%20consolidation%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20lower%20interest%20rate%20from%20a%20local%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-credit-unions%5C%22%3Ecredit%20union%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20I%20had%20a%20decent%20credit%20score%20and%20about%20%2418%2C000%20in%20student%20loans%2C%20and%20he%20had%20a%20poor%20credit%20score%20and%20about%20the%20same%20amount%20in%20consumer%20debt%20and%20car%20debt.%20He%20also%20had%20other%20small%20debts%20he%20had%20hanging%20around%20because%20he%20was%20a%20few%20years%20older%20than%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20agreed%20to%20each%20pay%20down%20our%20own%20debts%20before%20legally%20getting%20married%2C%20as%20poor%20credit%20scores%20could%20hold%20us%20back%20from%20getting%20the%20best%20interest%20rates%20when%20we%20bought%20a%20car%20or%20a%20home%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20we%20did%20to%20tackle%20Marshall's%20credit%20score%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fdebt-to-income-ratio%5C%22%3Edebt%20ratio%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20officially%20tying%20the%20knot%20in%20January%202021%20and%20eventually%20buying%20a%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20We%20solidified%20our%20budget%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20created%20spreadsheets%20for%20monthly%20and%20annual%20budgets%2C%20net%20worth%2C%20and%20retirement%20projections.%20We%20also%20made%20a%20list%20of%20every%20single%20debt%2C%20even%20tiny%20debt%2C%20such%20as%20a%20%2435%20bank%20overage%20protection%20that%20Marshall%20regularly%20used%20%E2%80%94%20it%20turned%20out%20that%20it%20was%20dinging%20his%20credit%20score%2C%20and%20he%20was%20paying%20a%20monthly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Foverdraft-fees-what-banks-charge%5C%22%3Eoverdraft%20fee%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20neither%20of%20us%20was%20aware%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarshall%20called%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fcredit-bureau-experian-equifax-transunion%5C%22%3Ecredit%20bureaus%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20check%20his%20credit%20record.%20It%20turned%20out%20a%20few%20inaccuracies%20were%20holding%20back%20his%20credit%20score%2C%20and%20he%20was%20able%20to%20get%20them%20deleted%20with%20just%20a%20phone%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20shopped%20around%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fbest-cheap-car-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Echeap%20car%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20more%20affordable%20phone%20plans%2C%20internet%2C%20and%20streaming%20services.%20It's%20worth%20it%20to%20shop%20around%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year.%20We%20saved%20%241%2C800%20annually%20just%20on%20our%20Xfinity%20internet%20bill%2C%20plus%20hundreds%20more%20by%20switching%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fnationwide-car-insurance-review%5C%22%3ENationwide%20car%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20we%20had%20our%20budget%20spreadsheet%2C%20goals%2C%20and%20research%20done%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20take%20action%20to%20streamline%20finances%20and%20minimize%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20We%20read%20a%20lot%20of%20books%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20to%20our%20local%20library's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-personal-finance-books%5C%22%3Epersonal%20finance%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%20section%20to%20browse%20and%20picked%20out%20any%20titles%20that%20corresponded%20with%20our%20current%20financial%20goals.%20Even%20if%20you%20only%20learn%20one%20thing%2C%20it's%20worth%20it%20to%20me%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20a%20certain%20author%20can%20phrase%20a%20complicated%20topic%20in%20a%20way%20I've%20never%20understood%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20books%20my%20husband%20read%20to%20become%20financially%20fit%20for%20marriage%20included%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3ERich%20Dad%20Poor%20Dad%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Robert%20T.%20Kiyosaki%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EThe%20Simple%20Path%20to%20Wealth%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20JL%20Collins%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EThe%20Total%20Money%20Makeover%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Dave%20Ramsey%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3ERetire%20Inspired%3A%20It's%20Not%20an%20Age%2C%20It's%20a%20Financial%20Number%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Chris%20Hogan%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EWealth%20Secrets%20of%20the%20Affluent%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Christopher%20R.%20Jarvis%20%26amp%3B%20David%20B.%20Mandell%2C%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EUnfu*k%20Yourself%3A%20Get%20Out%20of%20Your%20Head%20and%20Into%20Your%20Life%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Gary%20John%20Bishop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20We%20streamlined%20our%20other%20debts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20everything%20was%20organized%2C%20Marshall%20consolidated%20his%20remaining%20three%20loans%20%E2%80%94%20two%20high-interest%20credit%20cards%20and%20a%20high-interest%20car%20loan%20with%20separate%20banks%20%E2%80%94%20together%20into%20one%20personal%20loan%20from%20a%20local%20credit%20union%20with%20a%20much%20lower%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-loans%2Faverage-personal-loan-interest-rates%5C%22%3Einterest%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20single%20monthly%20payment%20that%20was%20lower%20than%20the%20former%20three%20combined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20this%20lowered%20his%20credit%20score%20slightly%20since%20he%20was%20taking%20out%20a%20new%20loan%20and%20also%20closing%20out%20his%20older%20loans.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20saved%20us%20lots%20of%20money%20just%20on%20interest%20alone%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20personal%20loan%20more%20quickly%20than%20having%20separate%20loans%20with%20higher%20interest%20rates%20through%20different%20providers%20with%20separate%20payments%20and%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20our%20finances%20are%20simplified%2C%20payments%20are%20easier%20to%20streamline%2C%20keeping%20our%20credit%20scores%20up.%20Saving%20money%20where%20we%20can%20allows%20us%20to%20to%20make%20extra%20debt%20payments.%20We%20use%20the%20avalanche%20method%2C%20meaning%20we%20pay%20off%20our%20small%20debt%20first.%20When%20we've%20paid%20it%20off%2C%20we%20add%20the%20small%20payment%20money%20to%20our%20next%20smallest%20debt%20until%20we%20get%20to%20the%20last%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-debt-consolidation-loan-credit-union-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726056782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.c