ofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvideo-of-malaika-arora-and-amrita-arora-visiting-mom-and-dad-last-night-goes-viral-after-anil-aroras-sudden-demise-fans-say-life-is-so-uncertain%2Farticleshow%2F113261256.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protest%20Outside%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20House%20Over%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Sikh%20Remarks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20BJP-backed%20Sikh%20group%20is%20holding%20a%20protest%20march%20to%20the%20residence%20of%20Congress's%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20in%20Delhi%2C%20objecting%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20in%20the%20US%20on%20religious%20freedom%20enjoyed%20by%20the%20community%20in%20the%20country.%20Contending%20that%20they%20are%20more%20secure%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%20than%20they%20were%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule%2C%20they%20are%20demanding%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20apologise%20for%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20three%20day%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20the%20fight%20in%20India%20is%20not%20about%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsking%20a%20Sikh%20member%20of%20the%20audience%20his%20name%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20is%20about%20whether%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Sikh%2C%20is%20going%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20wear%20a%20turban%20in%20India%3B%20or%20whether%2C%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Sikh%2C%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20wear%20a%20kada%20in%20India%3B%20or%20whether%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Sikh%2C%20is%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20a%20Gurudwara.%20That's%20what%20the%20fight%20is%20about%2C%20and%20not%20just%20for%20him%2C%20but%20for%20all%20religions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20have%20raised%20hackles%20back%20home%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20accused%20him%20of%20habitually%20making%20anti-national%20comments%20abroad%2C%20which%20is%20particularly%20serious%20now%20in%20view%20of%20his%20current%20position%20as%20the%20Leader%20Of%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20has%20called%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20comments%20%26quot%3Bsinister%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20spreading%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20narratives%26quot%3B%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20anti-Sikh%20riots%20of%201984%20following%20the%20assassination%20of%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20by%20her%20Sikh%20bodyguards%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20has%20been%20one%20time%20in%20our%20history%20when%20as%20a%20community%2C%20we%20have%20felt%20anxiety%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20insecurity%20and%20existential%20threat%2C%20it%20has%20been%20the%20times%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20family%20has%20been%20in%20the%20seats%20of%20power%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20comments%20have%20been%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Congress's%20secular%20credentials%20and%20its%20stance%20of%20religious%20freedom%2C%20its%20timing%20has%20been%20awkward%20in%20view%20of%20the%20anti-India%20narrative%20spread%20by%20a%20section%20of%20expat%20Sikhs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726054440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F05n7iat_rahul-gandhi_625x300_10_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsikhs-protest-march-outside-sonia-gandhis-house-over-rahul-gandhis-remarks-6540621%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20BJP-backed%20Sikh%20group%20is%20holding%20a%20protest%20march%20to%20the%20residence%20of%20Congress's%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20in%20Delhi%2C%20objecting%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20in%20the%20US%20on%20religious%20freedom%20enjoyed%20by%20the%20community%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsikhs-protest-march-outside-sonia-gandhis-house-over-rahul-gandhis-remarks-6540621%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Elections%202024%3A%20It's%20The%20Season%20Of%20'Others'%2C%20Once%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpamslj8g_elections_625x300_11_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20a%20week%20left%20until%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20parties%20and%20candidates%20have%20ramped%20up%20their%20campaigning%20efforts.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20parties%20are%20scrambling%20to%20finalise%20their%20candidates%2C%20with%20September%2012%20being%20the%20last%20date%20for%20nominations.%20Jharkhand%20and%20Maharashtra%20are%20expected%20to%20hold%20elections%20in%20November%2C%20following%20the%20October%20polls%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20states%2C%20'Others'%20-%20which%20includes%20smaller%20parties%20and%20independents%20-%20have%20either%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20governments%20or%20acted%20as%20spoilers%20to%20major%20contenders%20in%20the%20past.%20They%20could%20once%20again%20influence%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%202024%20state%20elections%2C%20particularly%20as%20major%20parties%20face%20internal%20dissent%20in%20Haryana%20and%20a%20rise%20in%20independent%20candidates%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20(2014)%20and%20Haryana%20(2019)%20resulted%20in%20hung%20assemblies.%20Jharkhand%20has%20seen%20hung%20verdicts%20in%20two%20of%20its%20four%20elections%20since%20its%20inception%20(2005%20and%202009).%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20in%20all%20three%20of%20its%20polls%20this%20century%20(2002%2C%202008%2C%20and%202014)%2C%20has%20never%20delivered%20a%20clear%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Haryana%2C%20two%20out%20of%20the%20five%20elections%20in%20this%20century%20(2009%20and%202019)%20resulted%20in%20hung%20assemblies.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20'Others'%20have%20averaged%20a%2025%25%20vote%20share%20and%20won%2034%2C%20representing%2012%25%20of%20the%20assembly's%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh%20Activity%20In%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202002%20elections%2C%20'Others'%2C%20including%20independents%20but%20excluding%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20National%20Conference%20(JKNC)%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20secured%20a%2030%25%20vote%20share%20and%20won%2022%20seats.%20The%20PDP%20and%20the%20Congress%20formed%20a%20post-poll%20arrangement%2C%20falling%20short%20by%20eight%20seats%20and%20relying%20on%20some%20of%20these%20independents%20and%20smaller%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202008%2C%20'Others'%20held%20a%2032%25%20vote%20share%20but%20won%20only%2010%20seats.%20The%20JKNC%20and%20the%20Congress%20then%20formed%20a%20government%20through%20a%20post-poll%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20'Others'%20won%2015%25%20of%20the%20vote%20and%20seven%20seats.%20The%20PDP%20and%20the%20BJP%20formed%20a%20government%20through%20a%20post-poll%20arrangement.%20In%20seven%20seats%2C%20the%20'Others'%20finished%20as%20runners-up.%20Notably%2C%20in%2012%20constituencies%20where%20'Others'%20were%20second%20runners-up%2C%20they%20garnered%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20'Others'%20won%20a%20seat%2C%20with%20an%20independent%20candidate%20defeating%20Omar%20Abdullah.%20They%20secured%2025%25%20of%20the%20vote%20and%20led%20in%2015%20of%20the%2090%20assembly%20segments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20last%20date%20for%20withdrawal%20in%20the%20first%20two%20phases%20passed%2C%20there%20are%20now%20458%20candidates%20contesting%2050%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20averaging%20over%20nine%20candidates%20per%20seat.%20This%20high%20level%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20first%20elections%20in%20a%20decade%20indicates%20intense%20competition%2C%20raising%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20hung%20assembly.%20The%20JKNC%20has%20minimal%20influence%20in%20Hindu-majority%20Jammu%2C%20while%20the%20BJP's%20impact%20is%20limited%20in%20Muslim-majority%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Haryana%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202000%20state%20elections%2C%20'Others'%20secured%2030%25%20of%20the%20vote.%20This%20decreased%20to%2020%25%20in%202005%2C%20rose%20again%20to%2030%25%20in%202009%2C%20then%20dropped%20to%2022%25%20in%202014%2C%20and%20further%20to%2018%25%20in%202019.%20They%20won%20between%20eight%20and%2016%20seats%20each%20time.%20In%202009%2C%20'Others'%20won%2015%20seats%20in%20a%20hung%20assembly%2C%20while%20in%202019%2C%20they%20won%20eight%20seats%2C%20excluding%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202009%2C%20the%20Congress%20formed%20a%20government%20with%20the%20support%20of%20independents%20and%20smaller%20parties%2C%20whereas%20in%202019%2C%20the%20JJP%20and%20the%20BJP%20struck%20a%20post-poll%20arrangement.%20'Others'%20finished%20as%20runners-up%20in%2012%20seats%2C%20and%20in%2016%20seats%20where%20they%20were%20the%20second%20runners-up%2C%20they%20received%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20'Others'%20did%20not%20lead%20in%20any%20assembly%20segment%20and%20garnered%20just%208%25%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20the%20local%20nature%20of%20state%20polls%20suggests%20they%20could%20still%20play%20a%20significant%20role.%20The%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20which%20has%20had%20a%20consistent%20vote%20share%20of%204%25-6%25%20in%20recent%20elections%2C%20has%20allied%20with%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%2C%20and%20Chandrasekhar%20Azad's%C2%A0Aazad%20Samaj%20Party%C2%A0(ASP)%20with%20the%20JJP%20to%20target%20Dalit%20votes%2C%20which%20constitute%2020%25%20of%20the%20population.%20In%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%2068%25%20of%20Dalits%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20supported%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20talks%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20failing%2C%20the%20AAP%20is%20likely%20to%20contest%20most%20seats%2C%20making%20the%20contest%20multi-cornered.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress's%20lists%20have%20triggered%20rebellion%2C%20with%20many%20MLAs%20and%20disgruntled%20leaders%20announcing%20their%20intentions%20to%20run%20as%20independents.%20These%20candidates%20could%20act%20as%20vote%20splitters%2C%20potentially%20diminishing%20the%20chances%20of%20dominant%20parties.%20Congress%2C%20favourite%20based%20on%20general%20election%20performance%20and%20initial%20opinion%20polls%2C%20should%20be%20cautious%20of%20'Others'%20who%20could%20split%20the%20anti-BJP%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJharkhand's%20Madhu%20Koda%20Precedent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202005%20elections%2C%20'Others'%20%5Bexcluding%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20and%20the%20BJP%5D%20achieved%20a%20remarkable%2050%25%20vote%20share%20and%20won%2025%20out%20of%2081%20seats%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20hung%20verdict.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%202009%2C%20'Others'%20maintained%20their%20strong%20performance%20with%20a%2049%25%20vote%20share%20and%2031%20seats.%20Although%20their%20influence%20waned%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20they%20still%20secured%20a%2033%25%20vote%20share%20in%20both%20elections%2C%20winning%2019%20and%2010%20seats%2C%20respectively.%20However%2C%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20and%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20achieved%20simple%20majorities.%20In%202019%2C%20'Others'%20were%20runners-up%20in%20eight%20seats%20and%20scored%20more%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20in%2031%20seats%20where%20they%20were%20second%20runners-up%2C%20affecting%20the%20chances%20of%20both%20alliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20is%20notable%20for%20electing%20an%20Independent%2C%20Madhu%20Koda%2C%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20in%202006%2C%20marking%20only%20the%20third%20instance%20of%20an%20Independent%20assuming%20such%20a%20role%20in%20Indian%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Bihar-based%20parties%20like%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%2C%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20had%20significant%20influence%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20but%20their%20impact%20has%20diminished%20over%20time.%20With%20the%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students%20Union%20(AJSU)%20aligning%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Jharkhand%20Vikas%20Morcha%20(Prajatantrik)%20merging%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20influence%20of%20'Others'%20may%20decrease%20in%202024.%20Many%20ST%20community-based%20parties%2C%20like%20the%20Jharkhand%20Party%2C%20have%20also%20seen%20a%20decline%2C%20with%20the%20JMM%20emerging%20as%20the%20main%20representative.%20Nevertheless%2C%20in%20a%20tightly%20contested%20election%2C%20'Others'%20could%20still%20play%20a%20disruptive%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumerous%20Players%20In%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201999%20and%202004%20elections%20produced%20hung%20assemblies%2C%20even%20as%20the%202004%20assembly%20was%20marginally%20hung%2C%20with%20the%20UPA%20falling%20five%20seats%20short%20of%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20'Others'%20won%2029%20seats%20with%20a%2024%25%20vote%20share.%20In%202014%2C%20they%20had%20a%2017%25%20vote%20share%20and%2020%20seats%2C%20while%20in%202009%2C%20they%20secured%2054%20seats%20with%20a%2032%25%20vote%20share.%20Parties%20such%20as%20the%20Bahujan%20Vikas%20Aaghadi%20(BVA)%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20the%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aaghadi%20(VBA)%2C%20the%20Peasants%20and%20Workers%20Party%20of%20India%20(PWPI)%2C%20and%20the%C2%A0Prahar%20Janshakti%20Party%C2%A0(PJP)%20have%20regional%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20'Others'%20influenced%2086%20seats%20(30%25%20of%20the%20total)%2C%20scoring%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20and%20affecting%20the%20chances%20of%20both%20major%20alliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Others'%20are%20poised%20to%20flex%20their%20muscles%20and%20may%20well%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%202024%20state%20elections.%20Whether%20they%20will%20become%20kingmakers%20or%20simply%20act%20as%20vote-cutters%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726054380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fu749rhi8_elections_625x300_11_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-others-aiming-to-be-kingmakers-in-2024-assembly-polls-6540893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Others'%20are%20poised%20to%20flex%20their%20muscles%20and%20may%20well%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%202024%20state%20elections%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Maharashtra.%20Whether%20they%20will%20become%20kingmakers%20or%20simply%20act%20as%20vote-cutters%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-others-aiming-to-be-kingmakers-in-2024-assembly-polls-6540893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2