rism%20among%20the%20biggest%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Economic%20Impact%20Assessment%20conducted%20by%20Nielsen%20for%20the%20ICC%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20mega-event%20held%20in%20October-November%20last%20year%20was%20the%20biggest%20ever%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20has%20demonstrated%20the%20significant%20economic%20power%20of%20cricket%2C%20generating%20economic%20benefit%20of%20USD%201.39%20billion%20(Rs%2011%2C637%20crore)%20for%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20Chief%20Executive%2C%20Geoff%20Allardice%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20ended%20India's%20unbeaten%20run%20in%20the%20tournament%20to%20win%20the%20trophy%20for%20a%20record-extending%20sixth%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20of%20tourism%20across%20the%20host%20cities%20amounted%20to%20USD%20861.4%20million%20of%20revenue%20generation%2C%20through%20accommodation%2C%20travel%2C%20transportation%20and%20food%20and%20beverage%20because%20of%20a%20massive%20influx%20of%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20tourists%20attending%20the%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20an%20ICC%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20secondary%20and%20incremental%20spends%20within%20the%20economy%20was%20a%20key%20driver%2C%20generating%20USD%20515.7%20million%2C%20which%20was%20approximately%2037%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20impact.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ICC%20did%20not%20specify%20whether%20the%20massive%20figure%20cited%20in%20the%20report%20is%20actual%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20record-breaking%201.25%20million%20spectators%20attended%20the%20mega%20event%2C%20of%20which%20nearly%2075%20per%20cent%20were%20attending%20an%20ICC%2050-over%20match%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20the%20report%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNearly%2055%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20international%20respondents%20had%20previously%20visited%20India%20regularly%2C%20whilst%20an%20injection%20of%20new%20visitors%20thanks%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%20saw%2019%25%20of%20international%20attendees%20making%20their%20first%20ever%20visit%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternational%20travellers%20visited%20multiple%20tourist%20destinations%20during%20their%20stay%20which%20amounted%20to%20an%20economic%20impact%20of%20USD281.2%20million%20and%20nearly%2068%20per%20cent%20of%20international%20attendees%20said%20that%20they%20would%20recommend%20India%20as%20a%20tourist%20destination%20to%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20the%20future%20further%20enhancing%20India's%20global%20image%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20statement%20from%20the%20governing%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2048%2C000%20full%20and%20part%20time%20jobs%20were%20created%20by%20the%20event%20through%20direct%20involvement%20in%20delivering%20the%20tournament%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20organisations%20across%20the%20hospitality%20sector%2C%20added%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20event%20created%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20and%20showcased%20India%20as%20a%20premier%20tourist%20destination%2C%20proving%20that%20ICC%20events%20not%20only%20engage%20fans%20passionately%20but%20also%20contribute%20significantly%20to%20the%20economies%20of%20our%20host%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20Allardice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726052940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fi8od59l8_jay-shah-rohit_625x300_11_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Frs-11-637-crore-iccs-mega-claim-on-what-economic-benefit-india-got-from-world-cup-6540828%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Economic%20Impact%20Assessment%20conducted%20by%20Nielsen%20for%20the%20ICC%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20mega-event%20held%20in%20October-November%20last%20year%20was%20the%20biggest%20ever%20ODI%20World%20Cup%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22cano