0Theoretical%20Computer%20Science%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20students%20demonstrated%20in%20front%20of%20the%20administration%20building%2C%20claiming%20that%20academic%20pressure%20from%20the%20classroom%20was%20the%20cause%20of%20their%20fellow%20student's%20demise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20protesting%20student%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDespite%20getting%20good%20marks%20in%20the%20examination%2C%20many%20students%20failed%20due%20to%20short%20attendance.%20In%20our%20batch%2C%20at%20least%20200%20students%20failed%20due%20to%20low%20attendance.%20This%20is%20unacceptable.%20One%20or%20two%20students%20might%20have%20done%20something%20wrong%2C%20but%20such%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20pupils%20can%20not%20be%20found%20on%20the%20wrong%20foot.%20The%20administration%20of%20IIT-Guwahati%20has%20created%20a%20toxic%20environment%20in%20the%20name%20of%20academic%20pressure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20third%20death%20in%20IIT-Guwahati%20this%20year.%20On%20August%209%2C%20exactly%20one%20month%20ago%2C%20the%20body%20of%20a%2023-year-old%20M.%20Tech%20student%20at%20the%20institute%20was%20found%20in%20her%20dorm%20room.%20She%20was%20a%20native%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20IIT-Guwahati%20authorities%20and%20police%20have%20launched%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20death%20of%20the%20student.%20Moreover%2C%20a%20series%20of%20mental%20well-being%20programmes%20were%20also%20started%20to%20help%20the%20students%20to%20deal%20with%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2020-year-old%20Bihar%20B.Tech%20student%20was%20also%20found%20dead%20in%20his%20hostel%20room%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726046400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fo085mge_iit-guwahati_625x300_11_September_24