%5C%22wp-image-365412%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESantosh%20Kumar%20Patel%20joined%20the%20police%20force%20despite%20the%20odds%20he%20faced%20growing%20up%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Santosh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20aspire%20to%20continue%20serving%20the%20public%20and%20better%20the%20image%20of%20the%20police%3B%20only%20criminals%20should%20fear%20the%20police.%20In%20my%20investigations%2C%20I%20ensure%20that%20innocent%20people%20are%20never%20put%20behind%20bars%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Santosh%2C%20who%20chose%20the%20pen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725977361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fdsp-santosh-1680878169-1725975712.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D365406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hailing%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20DSP%20Santosh%20Kumar%20Patel%20studied%20under%20kerosene%20lamps%20and%20lifted%20bricks%20for%20some%20food.%20Undeterred%2C%20he%20secured%20the%2022nd%20rank%20in%20MPPSC.%20Here's%20his%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Plugzmart%3A%20IIT-M%20Incubated%20Startup%E2%80%99s%20Fast%20EV%20Charger%20Takes%2030-45%20Mins%20to%20Charge%20Electric%20Cars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPlugzmart%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Chennai-based%20original%20equipment%20manufacturer%20(OEM)%20of%20EV%20chargers%20%E2%80%94%20obtained%20certification%20for%20its%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20charger%20from%20the%20Automotive%20Research%20Association%20of%20India%20(ARAI)%20late%20last%20month.%20ARAI%20is%20a%20research%20institute%20with%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Heavy%20Industries%2C%20which%20develops%20standards%20for%20vehicles%20and%20their%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20important%20development%20in%20advancing%20an%20indigenous%20EV%20infrastructure%20in%20India%20given%20how%20it%20has%20been%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F280479%2Findia-electric-vehicle-revolution-ev-charging-infrastructure-network-experts-future%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0unable%20to%20keep%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20the%20growing%20fleet%20of%20domestic%20EVs.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20indigenous%20manufacturing%20of%20its%20(charging%20infrastructure)%20key%20components%20is%20at%20a%20nascent%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20does%20the%20ARAI%20certification%20mean%20for%20Plugzmart%E2%80%99s%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20charger%3F%20This%20certification%20for%20the%20Chennai-based%20startup%E2%80%99s%20fast%20charger%20and%20proprietary%20controller%20card%20signifies%20their%20compliance%20with%20stringent%20operational%20safety%20standards%20and%20efficiency%20norms%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307090%2Fchennai-startup-builds-homegrown-iot-enabled-smart-ev-chargers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0back%20in%20December%202022%2C%20co-founder%20Ragavendra%20Ravichandran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20majority%20of%20EV%20chargers%20in%20India%20today%20are%20being%20imported%20and%20are%20of%20low%20quality.%20They%E2%80%99re%20largely%20imported%20from%20China.%20%5BThis%20is%20because%5D%20Chinese%20chargers%20are%20priced%20low%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20support%20from%20Chinese%20manufacturers%20once%20installed%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%2