D%20he%20exclaims%20as%20he%20retrieves%20the%20memory%20from%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20others%2C%20all%20involving%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%20childhood%20experience%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308752%2Fdodha-barfi-history-story-of-wrestler-harbans-vig-tales-of-taste-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20confectionery%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20out%20of%20flour%2C%20butter%2C%20milk%20and%20sugar)%20became%20an%20important%20guest%20at%20Shaheem%E2%80%99s%20home.%20It%20was%20the%20main%20celebrant%20on%20special%20occasions.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20included%20festivals%20and%20dinners%20when%20relatives%20would%20drop%20by%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20smile%20that%20suggests%20he%20would%20gladly%20binge%20on%20the%20dessert%20every%20day%20if%20he%20could%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eaficionado%20says%20it%20formed%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20growing-up%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20question%20begs%20to%20be%20asked%20why%20the%20natives%20of%20Kozhikode%20hold%20a%20reverence%20for%20this%20sweet.%20Shaheem%20credits%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20simple%20but%20unique%20taste.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20considered%20as%20an%20icon%20of%20Kerala%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Childhood%20friends%20(from%20L%20to%20R)%20Shabas%20Ahamed%20N%20C%2C%20Thesreef%20Ali%20P%20K%2C%20Sanu%20Muhammed%20C%20and%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%20started%20Fulva%20to%20retail%20authentic%20Kerala%20specialities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-me